[6] Media reports

Liberia: President sacks health minister
----------------------------------------
27 Aug 2014: (VOA) Liberian President Ellen Johnson Sirleaf has ordered the dismissal of some junior and senior level cabinet ministers, who, in the wake of the deadly EVD outbreak left the country and have yet to return ... [more]
http://allafrica.com/stories/201408270535.html

CDC: Q&A on EVD
--------------
29 Aug 2014: Members of the Young African Leaders Initiative (YALI) Network are focused on the EVD outbreak in West Africa and eager to learn more. More than 100 questions and comments came in from all over the region when experts at the US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) in Atlanta, Georgia answered questions from network members in a Facebook chat 26-28 Aug 2014. [A very short selection follows.]
https://youngafricanleaders.state.gov/cdcyalichat

